column2: On March 18, 2022, data for the Monthly New Motor Vehicle Sales Survey were corrected for reference period December 2020.
On May 26, 2021, data for the Monthly New Motor Vehicle Sales Survey were corrected for reference period January 2018 to December 2020.
Prior to 1953, data for Canadian and United States manufactured vehicles and overseas manufactured vehicles are not segregated.
Seasonally adjusted data for the New Motor Vehicle Sales survey are available for the period between January 1991 to February 2012.
